                    <PROP identifier="H" missing="no">
                      <PROPTEXT offset="2245">However much they want to help, if your loved ones have conspired to have you thrown in the slammer against your will - and many addicts will see it that way - you're hardly going to pop round to their place for a cuppa and a chat when you get out. Broken trust is not an easy thing to mend.    </PROPTEXT>
