              </AU>
              <AU>
                <PROP identifier="L" missing="yes">
                  <PROPTEXT offset="-1">If the addict may feel betrayed by his family and if feeling betrayed may cause one to get back on the gear again, it may be a recipe for the addict's getting straight back on the gear again.</PROPTEXT>
